wnby-desc: Forni information de detection per geolocalisation a patronos
wnby-geolocation-disabled: Le detection per geolocalisation ha essite disactivate per le usator.
wnby-geolocation-unsupported: Le detection per geolocalisation non es supportate per iste navigator.
wnby-geolocation-timeout-error: Le requesta de obtener le loco del usator ha expirate.
wnby-geolocation-permission-denied: Le usator ha refusate le requesta de geolocalisation.
wnby-geolocation-geoip-fallback: Le coordinatas de geolocalisation ($1, $2) ha essite resolvite per un servicio externe de [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IP_address_location localisation de adresses IP].
wnby-geolocation-geoip-no-fallback: Un tentativa de resolver le coordinatas de geolocalisation ($1, $2) per medio de un servicio externe non ha succedite.
wnby-no-fallback-location: Nulle loco de reserva es disponibile.
wnby-default-fallback-location: Uso del coordinatas predefinite como recurso.
wnby-invalid-coordinates-format: Le formato del coordinatas predefinite expecta un latitude, longitude.
wnby-localcache-use: Le datos ha essite recuperate ab le cache local del navigator.
